title: GORGEOUS CORNER UNIT IN REACH BCC!!
posting_body: ['Gorgeous and expansive 2/2.5 corner unit at REACH in Brickell City Center.', 'Unit features a wrap around balcony of 180 SF in its own.', 'Unit is 1265 SF with luxurious and modern finishes, and state of the art appliances.', 'Unit features 2 bedrooms with walk in closets.', 'Master bedroom features his/hers sink, bath tub and shower.', 'Washer and dryer inside unit.', 'Building is located in Brickell City center, building has direct access to mall.', 'There is a business center (computer desks and conference table) on the same floor, a few feet away from the unit.', 'Perfect for those that work from home.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!TEXT :', 'show contact info']
